<DocsLayout title="Equipment Tracking" section="Auxiliary Modules">
  <h2>Overview</h2>
  <p>
    Set up and manage equipment tracking in Field Promax. Track maintenance history,
    equipment inventory, and rental equipment with customizable fields.
  </p>
  <p>
    Field Promax's equipment tracking is highly customizable to fit your specific needs.
    Combined with the recurrence module, you have a powerful tool for ensuring timely
    maintenance. Use equipment reports to provide value to your customers.
  </p>

  <h2>How to Access</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Go to <strong>Settings</strong> → <strong>Manage Lists</strong> → <strong>Equipment List</strong></li>
    <li>Track, create, edit, or export equipment records as PDFs</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Setup</h2>

  <h3>Enable Equipment Tracking</h3>
  <ol>
    <li>Go to <strong>Settings</strong> → <strong>Company</strong> → <strong>Application Feature Settings</strong></li>
    <li>Locate <strong>Equipment Tracking</strong> and enable it</li>
  </ol>

  <h3>Define Custom Fields</h3>
  <img src="/images/auxiliary-modules/auxillarymodules_equipment_01.webp" alt="Equipment Fields" />
  <p>
    Set up <strong>Default Equipment Definition Fields</strong> and <strong>Default Maintenance Fields</strong>.
    These custom fields are automatically added to each new piece of equipment.
  </p>

  <h2>Managing Equipment</h2>

  <h3>Create Equipment</h3>
  <img src="/images/auxiliary-modules/auxillarymodules_equipment_02.webp" alt="Create Equipment" />
  <ol>
    <li>Click <strong>Create Equipment</strong></li>
    <li>Select a customer</li>
    <li>Enter relevant details and custom field values</li>
  </ol>

  <h3>Attach to Work Order</h3>
  <img src="/images/auxiliary-modules/auxillarymodules_equipment_03.webp" alt="Attach Equipment" />
  <ol>
    <li>Open a work order</li>
    <li>Go to the <strong>Equipment</strong> tab at the bottom</li>
    <li>Attach equipment created for the customer</li>
  </ol>

  <h3>Preventive Maintenance</h3>
  <p>
    Attach equipment to the <strong>Recurrence Module</strong> to manage preventive
    maintenance cycles automatically.
  </p>

  <h2>Mobile App</h2>
  <img src="/images/auxiliary-modules/auxillarymodules_equipment_04a.png" alt="Mobile Equipment" />
  <img src="/images/auxiliary-modules/auxillarymodules_equipment_04b.png" alt="Mobile Equipment Entry" />
  <ul>
    <li>Technicians can enter maintenance information after each cycle</li>
    <li>Create and attach equipment directly through the mobile app</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>History & Reporting</h2>
  <img src="/images/auxiliary-modules/auxillarymodules_equipment_05.png" alt="Equipment History" />
  <p>
    View maintenance history and details directly from the Equipment module.
    Export records as PDFs for customer documentation.
  </p>

  <h2>Notifications & Permissions</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Technicians:</strong> Can view and enter maintenance information via mobile app</li>
    <li><strong>Administrators:</strong> Can create and manage all equipment records</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Tips</h2>
  <div class="callout callout-tip">
    <p>
      <strong>Run Equipment Reports</strong> from the reporting module for detailed activity views.
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>Track maintenance records</strong> regularly to optimize equipment usage.
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>Use custom fields</strong> to capture information specific to your equipment types.
    </p>
  </div>
</DocsLayout>
